query.query:
select experiment.column.name, experiment.column.description
from experiment.column
where experiment.column.id in
    (select distinct experiment.timeseries_data.column_id from experiment.timeseries_data where experiment.timeseries_data.dataset_id={{dataset}})
query.name: Columns in the dataset

query.query:
select experiment.dataset.name as dataset_name, experiment.range_label.label_name as range_name, experiment.range_label.info as range_info, 
       experiment.dataset.date, experiment.institution.name as institution, 
       experiment.dataset.original_collector, experiment.dataset.type
from experiment.dataset
    inner join experiment.institution on institution_id=experiment.institution.id
    inner join experiment.range_label on experiment.dataset.id=experiment.range_label.dataset_id
where experiment.dataset.id={{dataset}} and experiment.range_label.id={{range_id}}
query.name: Dataset range metadata

query.query:
SELECT sample_no,
       MAX( case when column_id=1 then value else NULL end) AS time,
       MAX( case when column_id=2 then value else NULL end) AS voltage,
       MAX( case when column_id=3 then value else NULL end) AS current,
       MAX( case when column_id=4 then value else NULL end) AS energy_capacity,
       MAX( case when column_id=5 then value else NULL end) AS charge_capacity,
       MAX( case when column_id=6 then value else NULL end) AS temperature,
       MAX( case when column_id=7 then value else NULL end) AS step_time
FROM experiment.timeseries_data where dataset_id={{ dataset }} and sample_no%((SELECT MAX(sample_no) FROM experiment.timeseries_data where dataset_id={{ dataset }})/2000)=0
GROUP BY sample_no
order by sample_no
query.name: Dataset
